Cell["\<\
There are only 48 second-order conjoint (composite) inequivalent \
contributions with a one-body and a two-body vertex. The multiplicity check \
is fulfilled.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8895308415440407`*^9, 3.889530867561658*^9}, {
